-- Old Mutual's South African Money Manager Names Radley as Chief Executive
-- Vernon Wessels
-- 2010-06-17T15:31:32Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-17/old-mutual-s-south-african-money-manager-names-radley-as-chief-executive.html

          
          
             Old Mutual Investment Group South
Africa said it appointed Diane Radley, the finance director of
Old Mutual South Africa, as chief executive officer.  
 Radley will start on Jan. 1, 2011, London-based Old Mutual
Plc said in an e-mailed statement today.  
          
          


  


        